{"tid":1512732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖咀果日淋人黑油？","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:02:34.000Z","uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"826c99c02194d69efa716b7c0b1cc6f5ac2bc8e8","tid":1512732,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:07.000Z","msg":"在尖沙咀，有市民與示威者爭執，被淋黑油。<br />\n<br />\n晚上九時許，一批示威者在尖沙咀警署外聚集，有示威者指一名市民撞到人，包圍他要求道歉，又以鐳射光射他的面，之後有人用雨傘遮擋，多人毆打該名男子，旁邊有示威者阻止。<br />\n<br />\n之後見到男子臉部及上半身都被淋黑油，有人繼續向他射鐳射光，被打的男子說曾與一名穿反光衣的人有碰撞，期間有示威者不滿他的言論，所以被人襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n我比班藍絲圍啦<br />\n有冇手足當日在現場或者有片講下發生咩事？"},{"pid":"497fb5fad8d4361e3e68ef7c8b00acef8d47add9","tid":1512732,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d33d81943bfeac0eb23fefd021e90dc382bb89d","tid":1512732,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=ae3d6d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=c73d38e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=303dd520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4d77ad40f47e453045304123bd362fec620ce979","t